485
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:31,640
Sampai jumpa.

486
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:33,800
Sampai jumpa, Ko Song.

487
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:37,200
Saya.

488
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:39,800
Mau jalan-jalan naik mobil?

489
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:42,240
Kita masih punya tugas yang harus diselesaikan.

490
