Wow.

497
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,200
Dan jemput aku di pagi hari.

498
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:06,200
Bisakah kita bersepeda saja?

499
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:08,080
Terlambat. Kau telah kehilangan kesempatanmu.

500
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:10,080
Anda sudah kehilangan kesempatan itu, Tuan!

501
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:11,400
Ha ha ha ha.

502
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,320
Ayo pergi.

503
00:31:16,360 --> 00:31:16,840
Ayo.

504
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,920
- Pilih yang berbeda!
- Pilih yang berbeda!

505
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:36,080
