524
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:06,520
Tubuhku membutuhkan vitamin.

525
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,400
Begitu banyak alasan.

526
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:11,480
Aku mengizinkanmu masuk ke gengku,
