Jangan jadi penakut.

545
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:09,880
Argh!

546
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:13,920
Aduh.

547
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:15,960
Aduh!

548
00:34:20,040 --> 00:34:20,720
Kamu tertawa kan?

549
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:45,440
Dengan baik?

550
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,040
Sudah dapat tangkapan apa saja, Ko?

551
00:34:49,040 --> 00:34:50,760
Belum, Ayah. Dan aku bosan.

552
00:34:51,160 --> 00:34:53,160
