606
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:30,440
Mmm-hm.

607
00:39:31,640 --> 00:39:32,400
Oke.

608
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:36,160
Ayo, Orange. Pegang erat-erat.

609
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:37,280
Aku akan makan lebih banyak jeruk sekarang.

610
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,040
Agustus! Mata!

611
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:51,560
